    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Orisa leads with Fortify active to shrug off crowd control, using Energy Javelin to peel dive threats off her supports and Terra Surge to force the enemy off a contested point.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her damage output is low relative to other brawl tanks, so she relies on teammates to convert the space she creates rather than winning duels on her own.</p>"
